If you have access or can get these items: 1) ESD floor mat(secretaries hard mat) 2) wear non-conductive clothing and boots 3) use reduction spray for lessen ESD(starch based) 4) control the humidity(thermostat/humidifier) 5) ground yourself(touch metal to discharge) Oh yeah, all of the above can be quickly and easily done by use of the wrist strap.
There are disposble models now and overall, it does the job for 90% of the ESD dangers.
Doing the above will definetly control the remaining 10% or garner the assurance of ESD safety.
Read up on the topic.
